Package: formas
Title: FORMAS - Projects Data From A Swedish Government Research Council
    For Sustainable Development
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Markus", "Skyttner", , "markussk@kth.se", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: FORMAS provides daily updated open data about funded projects
    since 2006. This R package uses the open API at FORMAS to make data
    available for use from R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/KTH-Library/formas,
    https://kth-library.github.io/formas/
BugReports: https://github.com/KTH-Library/formas/issues
